Metadata.Title: Contract: Silence in Seattle
Metadata.Description: "A contract has been issued to you 47, and remember to follow the briefing we provided to you before you arrive. This is your true final test, and good luck. You must be a silent assassin," (training for SA on missions to players) "and you must remember to never get caught, or you fail. This final mission is in Seattle, away from our training facility. Good luck, 47."                                                                                -Diana Burnwood
